summary: The F-16 Fighting Falcon is an American fighter plane. It was made by General Dynamics for the U.S. Air Force. This fast plane can do many jobs, like fighting in the air and on the ground. It has great features like a clear canopy for better seeing and a special seat to keep the pilot safe. Though not new, it's still popular and used by many countries. Over 4,600 have been made since 1976, and it's known for its agility.
title: General Dynamics F-16 Fighting Falcon
